<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style2.css">
    <script src="../../public/js/bootstrap.min.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center container" id="div-login">
        <h2>Connectez-vous</h2>
        <div class="d-grid h-100">
            
            <div <% if (locals.error){ %> class="margin-40" <% } %>>
                <% if (locals.error){ %>
                    <div class="alert alert-danger  mx-auto">
                        <p><%= error %></p>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <form action="/login" method="post" class="w-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center gap-3">
                    <label class="d-flex flex-column">
                        Identifiant
                        <input type="text" name="login" id="login" required>
                    </label>
                    <label class="d-flex flex-column">
                        Mot de passe
                        <input type="password" name="password" id="password" required>
                    </label>
                    <button type="submit" class="mx-auto">Connexion</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <p>La connexion est accessible uniquement pour les administrateurs du site ; il est donc impossible de cr√©er un compte.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    

